- proper trace calls for `while` and `for` loops
- drawing of multiple separate trees
- drawing of multiple variables labels on the same node
- on code edit, rerun the code and go to the current step (i.e. live updates)
- show current variable values
- show syntax errors in the editor
- handle closure scopes
- allow setting breakpoints in the editor
- some sort of console to print messages to
- show current call stack when stepping
- animate transitions between steps
- support arbitrary graphs
